PrecisApprove the appointment by the Minister of Consumer and Corporate Affairs of Brian M. Black, of Edmonton, Alberta, as a member of the Standards Council of Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Arnold Pepper, whose term has expired.
